{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01MVdimC6DwuQoE1vuSJ4E6z","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The plan is:\n1. **Step1 kernel**: Add dTdt accumulation in the neighbor loop using SPH Laplacian of temperature: `dTdt += thermal_conductivity * (m_j/rho_j) * (T_j - T_i) * lap_W_visc(r_ij)`, write to `dTdt_out` array\n2. **step1.py**: Add `sorted_temperature` input and `dTdt_out` output to `compute_step1()`\n3. **Integrate kernel**: Add `sorted_dTdt` input, update temperature: `T += dTdt * dt - cool_rate * (T - T_ambient) * dt`, clamp to [0, 5000], write temperature to unsorted output\n4. **integrate.py**: Add `sorted_dTdt` input and `temperature_out` output\n5. **simulation.py**: Wire dTdt through pipeline\n6. **world.py**: Add `sorted_dTdt` buffer\n7. **Tests**: Heat diffusion correctness\n\nLet me start with the CUDA kernels."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":480,"cache_read_input_tokens":104174,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":480},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e6e8b27e-e279-4052-ba7d-ce90d33ff805","uuid":"380d05de-a467-4f2e-acbf-a640e13c34b4"}
